{"tid":1360920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真）提議鄉事委員會同村長參加元朗反恐遊行","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:37:58.000Z","uid":265766,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"658e10be78949475cc51983674285e0338865c9b","tid":1360920,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:59:27.000Z","msg":"元朗恐襲真係好恐佈，成班白衫人見人就打，再咁落去仲邊有人肯租村屋，開舖頭，或者入元朗挽，連仔女都唔咁認係圍村人。<br />\n為保村民面子，一定要同班亂打人嘅割蓆，參加遊行以表清白。上次畀人呃左要保家衛國，最後邊個要著草，邊個日日攞威？<br />\n侯志強同簡sir响光復上水時又派水又支持示威者，係好好嘅示範。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請認真考慮</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1979b710a7692270cdc0827b360ad95987a41d18","tid":1360920,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea60cf3ba90f28ead2ed40bfcaf395409f6d2bf","tid":1360920,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea96355067314ac639fa5af322a7fb55d544fee7","tid":1360920,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c770514734cd92c7a3df8b2b04134d291e926e17","tid":1360920,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"我正打算send email<br />\n事後同各位報告"},{"pid":"e635ab2722c339631bd82f7e9f6286682eae535b","tid":1360920